Jamieson Price https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jamieson_Price 0 Jamieson Kent Price is an American voice actor, best known for his deep and booming voice for numerous anime and video games. He is known as the voice of Lü Bu in Dynasty Warriors 5~8, Paul Phoenix and Heihachi Mishima in the Tekken series, Walter Bernhard in Castlevania: Lament of Innocence, Largo the Black Lion in Tales of the Abyss, Iron Tager from the BlazBlue series, the Count of Monte Cristo in Gankutsuou, Ovan in .hack//G.U., and Galbalan, the main villain of Ys: The Oath in Felghana and Milton Grimm from Ever After High. Price also had a part in the 2000 movie The Patriot. Jamieson_Kent_Price is an_American_voice_actor , best_known for his_deep_and_booming_voice for numerous_anime_and_video_games .
